The paper discusses the application of machine learning and deep learning methods in cybersecurity, specifically focusing on adversarial security attacks and perturbations. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CR (Cryptography and Security). The paper also covers topics related to machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), computer vision (cs.CV), and social and information networks (cs.SI).
